{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"344faefcb4302b08946b7c680383cb7580afef6d51fc7d860dab69fa8e11c50e","slug":"growth-employee","location":"/story/organization/growth_employee.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"当十八岁大一文科生成长为优秀的 AI 科技公司 CEO 助理……","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":2}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/story/organization/growth_employee.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/story/organization/growth_employee.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"growth_employee.md","url":"/growth_employee-f20007f3c8dc9fa4acad964b99bd5eb0.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"blockquote","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":4,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":4,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"作者：iGuoZ（量潮科技）\n来源：","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"lqyCoQ1KXj"},{"type":"link","url":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/3X1mTZ8PUIbGN_01Qkr5Jg","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"微信公众号原文","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"zwKsRRm3Xl"}],"urlSource":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/3X1mTZ8PUIbGN_01Qkr5Jg","key":"iOMh94Y0zN"}],"key":"bFqp24aH49"}],"key":"UhmaHuZAMR"},{"type":"thematicBreak","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"y4G26MNZlG"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"看到上一篇文章公司在组织新一个月的滚动招聘，写一篇关于人才培养与组织文化的品牌故事，从我的角度记录团队的成长和我的感受。","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"key":"fLoQJ66PRZ"}],"key":"mxEc6kL2kB"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"标题是助理本人的运营创意","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"QrEH2Bc2dY"}],"identifier":"id","label":"标题是助理本人的运营创意","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"BTMkfySIfe"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"上周末夜里，我的助理小周告诉我，她在尝试做自己的小红书账号，主题是“十八岁大一文科生误入 AI 科技公司担任 CEO 助理”。","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"key":"fFUfO8ewTE"}],"key":"nFd1gtwc52"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":10,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"她是学新闻传播的，做新媒体运营就是她的本专业。她说当时想起这个标题是觉得这个会火，然后果然一堆人在问怎么找到这个实习的，她哭笑笑不知道怎么回复。","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":10,"column":1}},"key":"iImsNzTi3P"}],"key":"RuWg5qFFUp"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"统一回复一下，看公众号上一篇帖子。CEO 助理一般从行政、项目这类管理职能庞杂的岗位选拔。","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"key":"Db2NSuuWFX"}],"key":"hetJuTZPJT"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1},"end":{"line":14,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"她大概是害怕我介意，特意强调了自己没有暴露公司信息。我的内心疯狂 OS，你怎么能不暴露呢！这都是可以转化的优质流量啊！！","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1},"end":{"line":14,"column":1}},"key":"SNGp7Xsyy8"}],"key":"yxJYfQWkN0"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"想了想没有给她更多要求。刚大一和刚来公司不到一个季度的职级 M1 新人，多给她一些空间慢慢发芽，而不是一下子就把她的创意压榨干净。","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"key":"mg6m2NHPuF"}],"key":"piex2dmr8s"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主要还是本人底子好，我的培养只是锦上添花","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"QZG3kR5az7"}],"identifier":"id","label":"主要还是本人底子好，我的培养只是锦上添花","html_id":"id-1","implicit":true,"key":"I2DEAD1xXv"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"实际上在我的战略规划里，“开打闭”是一个根本战略，能公开的都尽量公开。这次让我突然意识到，我该和团队强调这条根本战略了。","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"key":"hJcUAH1qFJ"}],"key":"olKwKBwadv"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在我的新媒体战略构想里，以公司账号群为中心、以核心成员的个人账号为卫星的新媒体矩阵是公司执行“开打闭”战略的主要传声筒。","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"t7xrqapbvJ"}],"key":"xqERHkgYsb"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当时听到小周说这个事情的时候，我的感觉是“这也太同频了吧”。看来我的战略还是设计得很自然的，刚好我的助理开始主动发起了这个战略。","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"key":"kkh2hVj2ms"}],"key":"ktc4oXGhHd"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CEO 助理最难的就是同频。年初刚招进来试用的时候我就十分惊叹，她居然能跟得上我的思考节奏。前面三任助理，两个升了总裁，一个升了秘书长，都没有她的反应速度快。","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"key":"bt2XZT3WJM"}],"key":"eCCCdvlVBo"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我从来都没有预期过我的助理能跟得上我的节奏，在我的设想中，至少得三到四个助理才能勉强跟得上我。目前的秘书处刚好处在这个编制规模，只是到了公司秘书长以上的级别我一般不会过多干预他们的日常管理，他们自己的节奏也基本上勉强可以跟得上我。","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"key":"V6xYna5Yg7"}],"key":"V0SLRs9ydC"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一个同频的 CEO 助理可以顶十个普通员工，二八定律永不过时。有了小周以后，我放心地把各种和团队沟通容易产生的摩擦都交给了助理处理，美名曰让她接触整个公司所有岗位（不是）。","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"key":"sXgvQYJwQ1"}],"key":"h8JdXy2P4W"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“淬火式”批量培养天才","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"l6wNfmPwLR"}],"identifier":"id","label":"“淬火式”批量培养天才","html_id":"id-2","implicit":true,"key":"PGFAzhUShx"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CEO 助理最重要的工作就是跟着我思考、帮我联系协调整个公司、补位所有缺人的岗位。哪里是 CEO 关注的重点，哪里就是 CEO 助理需要冲锋陷阵的。","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"key":"eJyVXXyPtQ"}],"key":"yn0ZifR7Vp"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在培养历任 CEO 助理的时候，我会非常强调“我的意图是什么”和反复问“你的思考逻辑是什么”。经过一两个月磨合以后，我带出来的助理都可以建立经营整个公司的基本思维。","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"key":"ullCXLWT0m"}],"key":"J1obYzmHTq"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"也正是因此，CEO 助理是公司晋升最快的一个岗位，目前的标准晋升路径是 M1 职级 CEO 助理 → M2 秘书长 → M3 副总裁 → M4 C Suite。","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"key":"zd9v04uutB"}],"key":"EqyLXf3S50"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我的 CEO 迟早也得让给他们，我已经感觉我要被我的团队淘汰进董事会养老了，虽然执行董事只有我一个，根本没什么董事会的概念。","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"key":"teQMXsOWen"}],"key":"rALmtYI3RD"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"天才们的成长从来都是靠自己的，我起到的作用主要是带领他们走他们本该走的路而已。","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"key":"EDxPWArIxB"}],"key":"b4a3zBKAu0"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"是否有可能标准化 CEO 助理的培养计划？","position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"key":"oItDop2shq"}],"identifier":"id-ceo","label":"是否有可能标准化 CEO 助理的培养计划？","html_id":"id-ceo","implicit":true,"key":"BOchaowrgk"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公司的一位社区伙伴听到我们讲我们的经验以后，说我们这种培养方式是“CEO 训练营”，说非常稀缺和难得。","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"key":"i3qqEdb0uv"}],"key":"QIrzHJ7HSE"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1},"end":{"line":42,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不过“CEO 助理训练营”是真的可行的。我听小周说她的帖子有互动的时候，首先想到的就是上线 CEO 助理训练营。","position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1},"end":{"line":42,"column":1}},"key":"XY8tZiCs36"}],"key":"qyllqVSADn"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":1},"end":{"line":44,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不过我在尝试做教学计划的时候发现，我的现行培养模式实在太精英化了，完全看被训练者能不能扛住。","position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":1},"end":{"line":44,"column":1}},"key":"HhzGVsBQNd"}],"key":"EVf4at9fsl"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1},"end":{"line":46,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我尝试把这些想法装进最近在建设的量潮第二大脑里（GitHub 仓库 quanttide/quanttide）。AI 给了我很好的建议，从 CEO 助理的日常工作里溯源，CEO 助理平时要做什么就应该教什么。","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1},"end":{"line":46,"column":1}},"key":"XM3G1XrQRN"}],"key":"fPlsEPND1S"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1},"end":{"line":48,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"很好，很产教融合。最近我把训练 CEO 助理的方法迁移到调教 AI，效果非常显著。现在我的日常工作已经变成了给 AI 指路一堆文档让 AI 自己读了自己写代码写文档。","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1},"end":{"line":48,"column":1}},"key":"jGAN9BTT3k"}],"key":"mTaSETCvqM"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":50,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不知道有没有市场。有的话就展开。最近千头万绪的也没有时间推进次要工作。","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":50,"column":1}},"key":"lZI1bhfiOD"}],"key":"FqcFb0RE6w"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":51,"column":1},"end":{"line":51,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为什么我不怕被手下们淘汰？","position":{"start":{"line":51,"column":1},"end":{"line":51,"column":1}},"key":"Q9EdRSrO3b"}],"identifier":"id","label":"为什么我不怕被手下们淘汰？","html_id":"id-3","implicit":true,"key":"PmOwe2Za1B"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":53,"column":1},"end":{"line":53,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我在他们这么大的时候，一个人和一个学院博弈了整整四年，完全靠个人能力和影响力苦苦支撑让量潮苟住，才有了十年以后的量潮的现在。","position":{"start":{"line":53,"column":1},"end":{"line":53,"column":1}},"key":"mC2CHmsXq9"}],"key":"nSMKKgkYJX"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":55,"column":1},"end":{"line":55,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我在他们这么大的时候，已经在一个学院老师集体唯唯诺诺不敢发言的时候和诺奖得主谈笑风生。","position":{"start":{"line":55,"column":1},"end":{"line":55,"column":1}},"key":"Q0rdOLT4nf"}],"key":"qELQrAuHF9"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":57,"column":1},"end":{"line":57,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"诺奖大佬说的每个话题，当时大三的我都可以非常流畅地接住，甚至可以随手拉出一篇正在读的论文说我刚好看过，看到老教授炫耀没有成功的可爱觉得特别好玩。","position":{"start":{"line":57,"column":1},"end":{"line":57,"column":1}},"key":"rAFNGUOaaT"}],"key":"bZZH06RrFp"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"直至今日我和诺奖得主的照片稳居学院本科生院史 C 位，教秘和辅导员们在每年的新生见面会都要 cue 我一下。","position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"key":"untVUENXHT"}],"key":"DMXGMCUbEQ"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":1},"end":{"line":61,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当然，众所周知的是，我只要一开始疯狂痛批厦大经济，立刻帖子就会传遍学校各个学院和各级毕业校友。","position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":1},"end":{"line":61,"column":1}},"key":"sRQcg2d9wP"}],"key":"sQlJ0jZTe6"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":63,"column":1},"end":{"line":63,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我带出来的团队取得的成绩，只会让我的牌子更响。无论是在校友圈、知乎圈、技术圈、学术圈等，我都影响过很多人的职业道路。","position":{"start":{"line":63,"column":1},"end":{"line":63,"column":1}},"key":"LUM1kFSffp"}],"key":"wc1cM8ywBm"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":65,"column":1},"end":{"line":65,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我听过不止一个客户说自己或者他们的朋友是因为看到我在知乎上的研究而对经济学产生强烈的兴趣，然后走上了经济学学术道路。但是我自己玩够跑路了哈哈哈哈（狗头）。","position":{"start":{"line":65,"column":1},"end":{"line":65,"column":1}},"key":"VWAdF162cu"}],"key":"wZgWqvRVQR"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":67,"column":1},"end":{"line":67,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"既然我在他们这么大的时候就可以打出自己的影响力，那么他们也可以。所以我反复在和我的手下和学生们强调，“你们还不够激进，还可以再大胆一点”。","position":{"start":{"line":67,"column":1},"end":{"line":67,"column":1}},"key":"zxLDNeTChX"}],"key":"z3vQRPpRUM"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":69,"column":1},"end":{"line":69,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"毕竟上面这些描述都不是当时的感受，而是事后长期的观察总结的积累。","position":{"start":{"line":69,"column":1},"end":{"line":69,"column":1}},"key":"Zed2SqY9YY"}],"key":"aJcGCd9VcI"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":71,"column":1},"end":{"line":71,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为什么厦大经济的院领导们可以被我骂破防？因为他们最引以为傲的学术，我真的有资格骂他们菜，而且他们没有资格反驳。","position":{"start":{"line":71,"column":1},"end":{"line":71,"column":1}},"key":"OEC9H56sFC"}],"key":"WKoHIUyqhI"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":73,"column":1},"end":{"line":73,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"要反驳？我大二拔尖计划的面试是怎么控场，怎么一个人在社保话题上吵赢五个老师的？（其实真相是我刚好在跟一个研究社保的老师的课题组）大四是怎么一篇结构实证的毕业论文五六个老师一个都看不懂的？","position":{"start":{"line":73,"column":1},"end":{"line":73,"column":1}},"key":"mFbUNN3GTg"}],"key":"hGtiMV3yEf"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":75,"column":1},"end":{"line":75,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"厦大经济总共才多少个老师？有几个能看懂我的毕业论文？我进入他们任何人的领域都很容易，但他们进入不了我的高计算机和数学技术还研究经济学根本问题的领域。","position":{"start":{"line":75,"column":1},"end":{"line":75,"column":1}},"key":"fIK9vQg7rs"}],"key":"YdnejqYQd9"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":77,"column":1},"end":{"line":77,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当年大三在拔尖计划的一次会议，现任院长时任副院长又开始宣传八高。当时我听了很多要好的研究生学长学姐吐槽老师不会教学生学不会，气不过想为他们发声，就直接贴脸开大“八高那玩意谁愿意学啊”。当时他脸都气绿了但说不出半句话。","position":{"start":{"line":77,"column":1},"end":{"line":77,"column":1}},"key":"amE615XJiG"}],"key":"xZ7IZSdhgI"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":79,"column":1},"end":{"line":79,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我说八高是废纸，八高就是废纸。我有亲身成长的经历作为标杆证明八高对学术研究能力的帮助很次要。","position":{"start":{"line":79,"column":1},"end":{"line":79,"column":1}},"key":"bXGj8YSE1A"}],"key":"DwqBXOMYpT"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":81,"column":1},"end":{"line":81,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"所以我凭什么不怕被淘汰？从来都是我卷别人，没有别人卷我的道理。这就是我的底气。","position":{"start":{"line":81,"column":1},"end":{"line":81,"column":1}},"key":"t8C9n1v7ql"}],"key":"cvOxj2uRZq"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":83,"column":1},"end":{"line":83,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"所以我在小红书和微信公众号发帖吐槽母校，可以说是“拿破仑回到了他忠实的法国”，只是激活了那些原本就属于我或者随时可以属于我的流量。","position":{"start":{"line":83,"column":1},"end":{"line":83,"column":1}},"key":"QHFXgNjU3o"}],"key":"aQy6cjt0Zb"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":85,"column":1},"end":{"line":85,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"去年年中的帖子火了以后，好多已经开始当老师的校友发现我们还在，联系上我们下单下到爆单，我们花了一两个季度才消化完。","position":{"start":{"line":85,"column":1},"end":{"line":85,"column":1}},"key":"zjqJFwm6nF"}],"key":"rCV9G3VUta"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":87,"column":1},"end":{"line":87,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一个能批量培养优秀领导者的元领导者，首先得是一个合格的标杆。我即是标准。","position":{"start":{"line":87,"column":1},"end":{"line":87,"column":1}},"key":"gJCw2fn0ZE"}],"key":"i5XVcvmTc8"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":89,"column":1},"end":{"line":89,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"所以我平时也特别鼓励我的手下和学生以挑战我为目标。我很清楚，我的价值不会因为在一两个领域被挑战而失去。毕竟还没有人可以同时在一百个领域挑战我，我倒是经常在一百个领域挑战这些领域的“权威”。","position":{"start":{"line":89,"column":1},"end":{"line":89,"column":1}},"key":"SFgv33zBEv"}],"key":"WiOqxYJ53A"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":91,"column":1},"end":{"line":91,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"现在的时代信息越来越发达。真正的权威是被挑战出来的，而不是靠学阀式的垄断获得的。","position":{"start":{"line":91,"column":1},"end":{"line":91,"column":1}},"key":"U8ic5JlxFS"}],"key":"GQqpNaYXAy"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":93,"column":1},"end":{"line":93,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这是我们要面对的现实，我们必须要把自己作为靶子给下一代领导者打，才能让他们站在我们的肩头成长。我们才能不变成我们讨厌的那种厦大经济式的学阀。","position":{"start":{"line":93,"column":1},"end":{"line":93,"column":1}},"key":"zC7rirdPYv"}],"key":"eudv9180k3"}],"key":"ARtIFSaJTR"}],"key":"fYcDGBw3xI"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}